    We have made the very tough decision to reduce the size of our company by approximately 9% and will be saying goodbye to some incredibly talented Asanas today and over the coming weeks.

    The Asanas that are departing are brilliant, creative, and collaborative innovators and leaders. They are our colleagues and our friends who have worked hard to help build Asana.

    We have a big mission that attracts mission driven people. They brought their ideas, expertise, and commitment to helping humanity thrive, and it's painful to part ways. I hope that many organizations and missions around the world will benefit from Asana talent in the future.
